  <name>Auto-Rotate</name>
  <summary>Deskew and turn upright every page of a PDF</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Auto-Rotate rasterizes a PDF, snaps each page to its correct orientation, corrects
      fine skew, and can binarize scans to crisp black-on-white, then reassembles the pages.
    </p>
    <p>
      Orientation detection and OCR rely on the Tesseract engine, which is not bundled in
      this Flatpak; deskew and the black-on-white cleanup work out of the box.
    </p>
  </description>
